query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM gestantes) as total_gestantes,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT gestanteId) FROM medicamentosGestacao WHERE tipo = 'polivitaminicos') as gestantes_com_polivitaminico,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM gestantes) - (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT gestanteId) FROM medicamentosGestacao WHERE tipo = 'polivitaminicos') as gestantes_sem_polivitaminico;
